   "author_association" : "CONTRIBUTOR",
   "body" : "This PR adds a new \"tx output spender\" index, and a new `gettxospender` rpc call which allows users to query which tx spent a given outpoint.\r\nSuch an index would be extremely useful for Lightning, and probably for most layer-2 protocols that rely on chains of unpublished transactions.\r\n\r\nThis PR can be viewed as an \"extension\" to https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/pull/24408 (which does the same thing but limited to mempool tx outputs).\r\n\r\nCode may need additional tests, but I wanted to collect ACKs/NACKs first (I'm aware that new indexes are not necessarily welcome additions)\r\n\r\nI chose to store an outpoint (32 + 4 bytes) -> txid (32 bytes) index (so -txospenderindex requires -txindex) rather than a outpoint -> disk pos index.",
